Antagony shook her head and looked around again. This bot wasn't very 
informative, so she'd have to find things out from somewhere else.

"No, that's good. Thank you." She said and looked at the Alliance base which 
they were approaching. She was eager to learn more about this planet, but 
she knew that the boring formalities of becoming a member of this faction 
would come first.
